description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'BURN 500 CALORIES with this 20 Minute Cardio HIIT Workout (No Equipment, No Repeats)' from the channel Nobadaddiction.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Do this 20 Min Cardio HIIT workout and burn 500 calories. Follow along from home without the need for any equipment. This is a full body workout to burn lots of calories and is great if you are trying to lose weight.
